  "detailed_description": "Wrap your brain around 76 levels of puzzling, golfing fun in Fort Golf, a puzzle mini-golf platformer. Many tricky obstacles complicate the quaint castle themed courses. With limited putts available, each level has a unique solution, which may not be as simple as it looks…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PUTT THROUGH CHALLENGING PUZZLES</h2><br>Navigate through shifting platforms, deadly spikes, scorching lava pools, and much more. Each set of levels brings new obstacles and mechanics to figure out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/65b95537c07ccf858fdd1f9682237710.poster.avif?t=1683638460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/65b95537c07ccf858fdd1f9682237710.webm?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/65b95537c07ccf858fdd1f9682237710.mp4?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND HIDDEN CHESTS</h2><br>Find chests scattered throughout the courses. Each one contains a unique item.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/d2985d3f92923feb4bc1e50413e5e675.poster.avif?t=1683638460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/d2985d3f92923feb4bc1e50413e5e675.webm?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/d2985d3f92923feb4bc1e50413e5e675.mp4?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECT SPECIAL ITEMS</h2><br>Change the look of your golf ball with collectible skins. Unlock bonus levels by finding keys. Teleport to new areas with magical runes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/8bc6deeba7c0f6de044441d9f7b1ee9f.avif?t=1683638460\" width=600 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE BONUS PUZZLES</h2><br>Figure out crafty new solutions to reach those gleaming treasure chests and reap the rewards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/e6e116e141c33e8365bc8e321d6be4ee.poster.avif?t=1683638460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/e6e116e141c33e8365bc8e321d6be4ee.webm?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/e6e116e141c33e8365bc8e321d6be4ee.mp4?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Wrap your brain around 76 levels of puzzling, golfing fun in Fort Golf, a puzzle mini-golf platformer. Many tricky obstacles complicate the quaint castle themed courses. With limited putts available, each level has a unique solution, which may not be as simple as it looks…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PUTT THROUGH CHALLENGING PUZZLES</h2><br>Navigate through shifting platforms, deadly spikes, scorching lava pools, and much more. Each set of levels brings new obstacles and mechanics to figure out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/65b95537c07ccf858fdd1f9682237710.poster.avif?t=1683638460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/65b95537c07ccf858fdd1f9682237710.webm?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/65b95537c07ccf858fdd1f9682237710.mp4?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND HIDDEN CHESTS</h2><br>Find chests scattered throughout the courses. Each one contains a unique item.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/d2985d3f92923feb4bc1e50413e5e675.poster.avif?t=1683638460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/d2985d3f92923feb4bc1e50413e5e675.webm?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/d2985d3f92923feb4bc1e50413e5e675.mp4?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECT SPECIAL ITEMS</h2><br>Change the look of your golf ball with collectible skins. Unlock bonus levels by finding keys. Teleport to new areas with magical runes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/8bc6deeba7c0f6de044441d9f7b1ee9f.avif?t=1683638460\" width=600 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE BONUS PUZZLES</h2><br>Figure out crafty new solutions to reach those gleaming treasure chests and reap the rewards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/e6e116e141c33e8365bc8e321d6be4ee.poster.avif?t=1683638460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/e6e116e141c33e8365bc8e321d6be4ee.webm?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358570/extras/e6e116e141c33e8365bc8e321d6be4ee.mp4?t=1683638460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
